From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Mon, 18 Nov 2024 14:53:42 -0800
Subject: perf trace-event: Always build trace-event-info.c
Git-commit: 800c93ffaf943a8c6d7c90d4e0468b9431e3dd7a
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

trace-event-info.c has no libtraceevent dependencies, always build it
and use it in builtin-record and perf_event_attr printing.

